About Us
We believe in small teams with high impact. Passionate about gaming and making video games for 20+ years. Headquartered in sunny Newport Beach, CA and development offices in Kyiv, Ukraine.
Nowadays our games have 200+ million downloads combined
Vast experience, different genres, different audiences, all platforms
Flat structure. Everybody's opinion counts
Great atmosphere and work-life balance. And the barbecue on the roof
